Lord, I want my life to count — not for my own glory but for Yours. Use everything I am and everything I have been through for the purpose You had in mind before I was born. Amen.', NULL, false) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
Lord, I have spent time grieving paths that closed and doors that did not open — help me to trust that what looked like a detour was actually redirection toward what You always intended.
